Snarl's rockets nailed into Caliburst, and sent the gun flying off of
the tank. He landed in a bush with a thud. Grimlock transformed, and
stood up, getting ready to fire a rocket from his gun. He leveled it,
but got slammed in the chest by the distabyliser ray, which sent funny
signals into his brain, causing him to step awckwardly a few times. He
stepped once to many, and began to fall backwards, then hit the ground
hard, as the impact caused his rockets to go off, to his right, into the
pack of Autobots.

Cliffjumper eyes widdened when he saw one of the rockets heading towards
him and Pacifix, and jumped at Torca, trying to tackle him out of the
way.
